import * as React from 'react'
import Toolbar from '@mui/material/Toolbar'
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import AOS from 'aos'
import { useEffect } from 'react'
import { AppBar, Box, Container, Grid2, Link } from '@mui/material'

// Styling the Navbar text
const NavbarText = styled(Typography)`
  color: white;
  font-family: 'poppins';
`
const TopBar = styled(Box)`
  background-color: black;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  height: 44px;
  /* display: none; */
`

const NavbarMaintext = styled(Navbar)`
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
`
const Navbartext = styled(Typography)`
  font-family: 'Poppins';
`

const Bartext = styled(Grid2)`
  display: flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items: center;
  
`


export default function Navbar () {
  useEffect(() => {
    AOS.init({
      duration: 2000
    })
  }, [])

  return (
    <>
      <TopBar>
        <Toolbar>
          <NavbarText>
            Summer Sale: All Swim Suits And Free Express Delivery - OFF 50%!
            Shop Now
          </NavbarText>
        </Toolbar>
      </TopBar>
      <AppBar>
        <Container>
          <Grid2 container>
            <Grid2 size={4}>
              <Typography variant='h4'> Exclisive </Typography>
            </Grid2>

            
              <Bartext size={5}>

                <Box>
                <Navbartext></Navbartext>
                  <Link href='#' underline='hover' sx={{ color: 'white' }}>
                    Home
                  </Link>
                </Box>
                <Box>
                  <Link href='#' underline='hover' sx={{ color: 'white' }}>
                    Contact
                  </Link>
                </Box>
                <Box>
                  <Link href='#' underline='hover' sx={{ color: 'white' }}>
                    About
                  </Link>
                </Box>
                <Box>
                  <Link href='#' underline='hover' sx={{ color: 'white' }}>
                    Sign Up
                  </Link>
                </Box>

              </Bartext>
      -
          </Grid2>
        </Container>
      </AppBar>
    </>
  )
}
